description:
Goodlato launches our new product, "Ugly Sorbets".

Now listen! Approximately 20% of produce or more gets thrown out for cosmetic reasons like weird shapes, odd colors and blemishes. To fight against unnecessary food waste, we partnered with sustainable brands to source these "ugly" berries to turn into tasty and refreshing sorbets, in Goodlato style. Because not only are we committed to making our products low in calorie and low in sugar for a health-driven cause, we are also committed to sustainability, and this will always be in Goodlato's DNA. 

Get the first taste of our Ugly Sorbets on
21st August, 11.30am - 2.30pm at @treatsure pop up at their concept store! 

#treatsuresg #goodlato #lowcalorie #sustainable #produce #sustainablesg

description: There were many sleepless nights, days filled with doubts and disappointments (there still is), but thanks for all the support thus far! Hope that Goodlato will be here for the long run.

Ventrickle X Goodlato

Stories shape who we are.

Youâ€™ll know we here at Ventrickle are big fans of knowing what goes into your food and choosing healthier, low calorie options that help keep you lean.

Our friend Van, has an amazing story to tell. Passionate and dedicated to delivering a healthy, lower calorie experience, with all the goodness of gelato, check out her labour of love - Goodlato.

Best of all? She learnt to do it herself. 

High in protein, low in sugar, Goodlato is all about creating the ultimate satisfied craving for you.

Weâ€™re proud to call Van a partner in the mission for better health. 

Why not swing by and try it for yourself? Healthy eating need not be restrictive. Vanâ€™s very own Vanilla bean gelato is under 300 calories, for good measure.

description: Itâ€™s day one of our menu revamp. Hereâ€™s a new flavour drop for you guys - Strawberry Sakura ðŸŒ¸ keep a lookout for our other new flavours in the coming weeks!

At Goodlato, we make outrageous and unique flavoured gelato with â€œgoodâ€ calories. Ube is one of them. Ube is a Philippine dessert made from boiled purple yam. We love challenges, hence our extravagant flavours are all ironically low in calories. At 360 calories/pint, we believe we did the impossible.
caption: Photo by Ice Cream Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato on November 08, 2022.

description: We recently had someone mention that our gelato will never be the same as traditional gelato. Weâ€™d be lying if we say that in a side by side comparison, ours would be creamier. Of course, with 4 times as much fat content, traditional gelato carries a heavier and creamier texture. But we believe we do a pretty good job at creating something insanely close to the original. Whatâ€™s more, creamier isnâ€™t always better! As an avid gelato lover, there are times when gelato can come across as overwhelmingly sweet and too rich - to the point of being â€œjelakâ€ and sickeningly heavy. Goodlato strikes the right balance and we believe thereâ€™s a crowd out there whoâ€™d frankly choose our rendition over the other. So yes, our gelato will never be the same as traditional gelato. But thatâ€™s okay, because truthfully, we might even be better. ðŸ«¢ (Disclaimer - Traditional gelato is incredibly delicious, we just want to stress that Goodlato is equally good and can do without the comparisons, come give us a try and see what we mean!)

description:
[Goodlato]
We are probably all fans of gelato, but it's even more enticing and less sinful when they are high in protein and low in sugar & fat content! They actually state the calories of each flavour so you can eat with less guilt knowing it's much lower than other usual gelatos!

Ube 
This was definitely my favourite flavour, as the ube was quite strong and not too sweet!

Pistachio 
Pistachio was definitely evident here, and it's the milky kind rather than the nuttier ones, altho it's still quite enjoyable!

Ruby Pink Milk Choco
This was pretty similar to what you'd get from milk choc, and I especially liked the pretty pink colour ðŸ¤­.

Earl Grey Lavender
Both earl grey and lavender were q prominent! Defo for lovers of these 2 flavours. 

Do head down early as most popular flavours are usually sold out by evening! ðŸ¤­

Thank you Vanessa @goodlato for inviting and hosting us!
